### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8087

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------
### Offers
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------

### Get offers for a platform (JSON)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/offers/CryptoTrading.com

### Get offers for a platform (XML)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/offers/CryptoTrading.com
Accept: application/xml

### Get offers filtered by product type
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/offers/CryptoTrading.com?productFilter=["Crypto","ETF"]

### Get offers filtered by max yearly fee
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/offers/CryptoTrading.com?maxYearlyFeeFilter=25

### Get offers with both filters combined
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/offers/CryptoTrading.com?productFilter=["Crypto"]&maxYearlyFeeFilter=50

### Get offers with both filters combined (XML)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/offers/tradeCom.co.uk?productFilter=["Share","ETF"]&maxYearlyFeeFilter=50
Accept: application/xml

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------
### Signup
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------

### Sign up a new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "packageId": 1,
    "firstName": "John",
    "lastName": "Doe",
    "username": "johndoe",
    "email": "john.doe@example.com",
    "hashedPassword": "password123",
    "address": "Fantasy Lane 34 Chicago USA",
    "origin": "offerservice"
}

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------
### Version
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------

### Get version (plain text)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/version

### Get version (JSON)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/version
Accept: application/json
